        <h2 class="nhsuk-heading-m">When these terms apply</h2>

        <ol>
          <li>Please read these terms of use and our
          <a href="/privacy-policy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">privacy policy</a>,
          <a href="/cookies" target="_blank" rel="noopener">cookies policy</a> and
          <a href="/accessibility-statement" target="_blank" rel="noopener">accessibility statement</a>.
